<p>Austrian artist Thomas Medicus&#8217; 2014 anamorphic sculpture <em>Emulsifier</em> arranges 160 hand-painted glass strips to present each of four different images, depending on the viewer&#8217;s perspective.</p>
<p><em>Head Instructor</em>, below, uses the same technique. <a href="https://www.thomasmedicus.at/en/index.php">More at his website.</a></p>
